    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1766436296\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与醉酒的羊驼一起探索超现实世界！解决谜题，从河里捞出最奇怪的物品，与西瓜小混混战斗，并找到这个世界的所有秘密！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/65f0cbd0b80c7044f60741fc8ce1c6a8.poster.avif?t=1766436296\" width=428 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/65f0cbd0b80c7044f60741fc8ce1c6a8.webm?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/65f0cbd0b80c7044f60741fc8ce1c6a8.mp4?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>喝。喝你找到的一切。这款游戏没有禁酒令！<br></li><li>超过40个疯狂的任务。有些可能看起来很奇怪，你永远不知道会发生什么。<br></li><li>找到所有30顶有趣的帽子。<br></li><li>把炸弹扔进传送门，炸毁岩石，焚烧你的敌人！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/37eb2b050c1daae74cc3cf8cd06476e9.poster.avif?t=1766436296\" width=776 height=504 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/37eb2b050c1daae74cc3cf8cd06476e9.webm?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/37eb2b050c1daae74cc3cf8cd06476e9.mp4?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>胡萝卜人？醉酒的蝴蝶？还是地狱小鸡？认识这个世界的所有居民。<br></li><li>钓鱼！河里不仅仅有鱼。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/07a2bede06dcbeb9ee4a0500c226108c.poster.avif?t=1766436296\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/07a2bede06dcbeb9ee4a0500c226108c.webm?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/07a2bede06dcbeb9ee4a0500c226108c.mp4?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>我们的主角是一只可爱的羊驼！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/47445603856a0a1659bc1533feb3793b.poster.avif?t=1766436296\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/47445603856a0a1659bc1533feb3793b.webm?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820100/extras/47445603856a0a1659bc1533feb3793b.mp4?t=1766436296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
